  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The researchers propose to study the airways of asthmatics given TPI ASM8 for 14 days, and
      examine the protective effects on allergen-induced bronchoconstriction, hyperresponsiveness
      and airway inflammation.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Early and late asthmatic responses were attenuated by ASM8 and by placebo
      solution.Methacholine challenge was not affected by study medication. Other parameters were
      unchanged.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
